claim.claim-text:
4. A power cord with a safety device, comprising: 
two power lines arranged in parallel; 
an insulating internal sheath layer covering the power lines; 
a conductive sheath material provided around said internal sheath layer; 
an insulating external sheath layer forming a cord contact portion by covering said conductive sheath material; and 
a plug containing a power shutdown device operating upon detection of a current flowing through said conductive sheath material.
